{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_06_03",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 06 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "さて、すみれちゃんのご家族の了承を得たところで\nもっと具体的にいろいろ詰めていこか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that we have Sumire-chan's family's approval‚\nlet's get down to the specifics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "町おこしイベントの日程決めんとやし\nのんびりしとられへん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to decide on the date for the town revitalization event‚\nso we can't relax.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、何をすればいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ what should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 17.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに必要な機材とスタッフを集めないと\nそれに会場の手配、宣伝、沢山あるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to gather the equipment and staff for the live performance‚\narrange the venue‚ advertise‚ there's a lot to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 25.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "要は今まで事務所がやってくれてたこと、全部やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Basically‚ everything the agency used to do for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、考えただけで、目が回りそう……\n歌やダンスの練習だってしないといけないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ just thinking about it makes me dizzy…\nAnd we still have to practice singing and dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、やるって決めたんだから、頑張るよ！\n私に出来ること、なんだってやってみせるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm determined to do it‚ so I'll work hard!\nI'll try my best at anything I can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 46.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、気持ちはめーっちゃ嬉しいけど、心配無用や\nそこはすでに手を打ってあるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I'm happy you're so enthusiastic‚ but there's no need to worry.\nI've already taken care of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 58.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私達、こっちに来る前にね、実は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We‚ before we came here‚ actually――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私に山形での活動をバックアップしてほしい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want me to support your activities in Yamagata?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私達のプロデューサーでもない姫野さんに\nこんなことをお願いするのは、心苦しいのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It's hard for me to ask this of you‚ Himeno-san‚\nsince you're not our producer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 76.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします～\nうちら、姫野さんだけが頼りなんです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please~\nYou're our only hope‚ Himeno-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "随分、難しいことを言うのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's quite a difficult request…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そこまでして、山形に行く必要はあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it really necessary to go to Yamagata?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私達にはすみれが必要なんです\nだから、すみれの問題を解決するために……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. We need Sumire.\nThat's why‚ to solve her problem…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一つ、訊かせて頂戴。すみれを助ける理由は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me ask you something. The reason you're helping Sumire",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "仲良しだから？　それとも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is because you're friends? Or…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "仲良しだから、じゃありません\n私達の仲間、だからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not because we're friends.\nIt's because she's our friend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEが頂点に立つために\nすみれは絶対に必要なメンバーです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For TRINITYAiLE to reach the top‚\nSumire is an absolutely essential member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。トリエルにとって、山形での活動は\n大きな意味がある、いうことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. For TRINITYAiLE‚ our activities in Yamagata\nhold great significance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………ふうん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Hmm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……いいでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "社長にはうまいこと言っておくわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll smooth things over with the president.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "支援する許可を、私が取ってあげましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll get you permission for support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……っ！　ありがとうこざいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…! Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……貴方達、TRINITYAiLEに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can't let TRINITYAiLE‚ you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "無様なステージをさせる訳には、いかないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "perform on a pathetic stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.6333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
