      "text": "……いくらなんでも、急過ぎやけどね\nさ、すみれちゃん、これから忙しくなるよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's way too soon‚ no matter how you look at it.\nWell‚ Sumire-chan‚ are you ready to get busy?",
